  <brief_title>Local Analgesia in Knee- and Hipatroplastic Surgery in Patients With Rheumatic Disease: Extra- vs. Intracapsulare Position of Catheter</brief_title>
  <official_title>Local Analgesia in Knee- and Hipatroplastic Surgery in Patients With Rheumatic Disease: Extra- vs. Intracapsulare Position of Catheter</official_title>
